{"id":885,"date":"2025-11-24T11:53:27","date_gmt":"2025-11-24T10:53:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/?page_id=885"},"modified":"2025-12-09T14:54:54","modified_gmt":"2025-12-09T13:54:54","slug":"home","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/","title":{"rendered":"Home"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"hero full-screen\" style=\"background-image: url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/home.jpg')\" id=\"welcome \">\r\n    <video preload=\"metadata\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\">\r\n        <source src=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/home.mp4\" type=\"video\/mp4\">\r\n    <\/video>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12-8 col-m-12-2\">\r\n                                <h1>We bring ideas to light.<\/h1>\r\n                <p><\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"bg-white padding overflow\" id=\"aboutus\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-12-8 col-m-12-2\">\r\n                    <h2>About<\/h2>\r\n                    <p><p>The Art of Light is an international light design agency that specializes in unforgettable light experiences for live shows and events. With over 15 years of global expertise, we are your trusted partner in creating long-lasting memories.<\/p>\n<p>Driven by a passionate team of highly-skilled professionals, we add another dimension to the music. From sketch to show, we bring ideas to light.<\/p>\n<\/p>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n        \n\n\r\n<div class=\"full-screen\" data-parallax=\"mediaScroller\" data-parallax-backgrounds=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/artist-1.jpg,https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/artist-2.jpg,https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/artist-3.jpg\" id=\"our-portfolio\">\r\n    <div class=\"scroller\">\r\n                <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/artist-1.jpg\" alt=\"1\">\r\n                <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/artist-2.jpg\" alt=\"1\">\r\n                <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/artist-3.jpg\" alt=\"1\">\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                                <div class=\"col-12-5 col-ml-12-1 col-mr-12-6\">\r\n                                        <h2>Portfolio<\/h2>\r\n                    <p>From spectacular festivals to intimate theatre shows, we love it all. Our designs create incredible and long-lasting memories for every audience. Experience some of our recent projects and signature shows.<\/p>\r\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/portfolio\" class=\"ui button special\">\r\n                        Check our portfolio                    <\/a>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"bg-white padding\" id=\"design\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n                        <div class=\"row\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"col-12-5\">\r\n                        <div><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/design.png\" alt=\"Design\"><\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                    <div class=\"col-12-7\">\r\n                        <h2>Design<\/h2>\r\n                        <p><p>We strive to create innovatory and out-of-this-world designs. Achieved by challenging ourselves to keep evolving and learning, you can never be done learning. We naturally keep an eye on new developments and trends, because light is our passion. Our team is one of our strengths. We keep our skills sharp, by working together, asking for feedback and being critical, to insure high quality.<\/p>\n<\/p>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        \n\n    <div class=\"bg-white padding\" id=\"program\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n                            <div class=\"row row-reverse\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"col-12-5\">\r\n                        <div><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/program.png\" alt=\"Program\"><\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                    <div class=\"col-12-7\">\r\n                        <h2>Program<\/h2>\r\n                        <p><p>On location or in our own studio, we always make sure that we are prepared properly. Programming is an important element for a next level light show, a preparation we do not take lightly. Whatever challenge we face, we get the job done.<\/p>\n<\/p>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        \n\n    <div class=\"bg-white padding\" id=\"perform\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n                        <div class=\"row\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"col-12-5\">\r\n                        <div><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/perform-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Perform\"><\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                    <div class=\"col-12-7\">\r\n                        <h2>Perform<\/h2>\r\n                        <p><p>This is the moment where everything comes together, and you see a vision come to life. We perform a next level light show, every time we are behind the tables. Creating the ultimate experience &#8211; not only for the audience, but everyone involved \u2013 is what makes our hearts race.<\/p>\n<\/p>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        \n\n<div class=\"bg-white padding overflow\" id=\"meet-our-team\">\r\n    <div class=\"visual-stagelight\" data-parallax-speed-x=\"-3vw\"><\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-12-6\">\r\n                <p><strong><h1>Meet our team<\/h1>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\r\n                <p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n                <p>In the studio and on the road, the team of freelancers and full-timers Rik, Romy, Maxim and Andr\u00e9 work together with passion to ensure quality, professionality, creativity and consistency. Our strength is our team and the passion we all share \u2013 LIGHT.<\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-12-6\">\r\n                <p><\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<div class=\"bg-white padding-big-bottom\">\r\n    <ul class=\"grid random staff bg-matte\">\r\n                        <li style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/TAOL_New_Andre.png')\">\r\n            <div>\r\n                <div class=\"name\">Andr\u00e9<\/div>\r\n                <ul class=\"functions\">\r\n                    <li>Founder &#038; Creative Director<\/li>\r\n                <\/ul>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/li>\r\n                <li style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Project-Achtergrond-verwijderen.png')\">\r\n            <div>\r\n                <div class=\"name\">Romy<\/div>\r\n                <ul class=\"functions\">\r\n                    <li>Director of Operations<\/li>\r\n                <\/ul>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/li>\r\n                <li style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Profielfotos-team-6.png')\">\r\n            <div>\r\n                <div class=\"name\">Kasper<\/div>\r\n                <ul class=\"functions\">\r\n                    <li>Light Designer &#038; Operator<\/li>\r\n                <\/ul>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/li>\r\n                <li style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/TAOL_New_Rik.png')\">\r\n            <div>\r\n                <div class=\"name\">Rik<\/div>\r\n                <ul class=\"functions\">\r\n                    <li>Light Operator<\/li>\r\n                <\/ul>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/li>\r\n                <li style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/TAOL_New_Lindsay.png')\">\r\n            <div>\r\n                <div class=\"name\">Lindsay<\/div>\r\n                <ul class=\"functions\">\r\n                    <li>Finance<\/li>\r\n                <\/ul>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/li>\r\n                <li style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Profielfotos-team-5.png')\">\r\n            <div>\r\n                <div class=\"name\">Maxim<\/div>\r\n                <ul class=\"functions\">\r\n                    <li>Production Manager<\/li>\r\n                <\/ul>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/li>\r\n            <\/ul>\r\n<\/div>\n\n\r\n<div class=\"bg-white padding overflow\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-full\">\r\n                <h2>An experience worth sharing.<\/h2>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<div class=\"bg-white padding\">\r\n    <ul class=\"instagram padding\">\r\n                <li><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DA8R2kYqzLM\/\"><\/blockquote><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DCGlBheKW5t\/\"><\/blockquote><\/li><li><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/C-r5Gs7KlIW\/\"><\/blockquote><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DI_woFLKeR0\/\"><\/blockquote><\/li><li><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/BYhiTIPgrf6\/\"><\/blockquote><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DI1XzdMqSvW\/\"><\/blockquote><\/li><li><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DQomhjbDf5g\/?img_index=2\"><\/blockquote><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/B8MOfIJFc-c\/\"><\/blockquote><\/li><li><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/C6tnL7JqS-g\/\"><\/blockquote><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-version=\"8\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DKg0bNtKkPs\/\"><\/blockquote><\/li>            <\/ul>\r\n<\/div>\n\n\r\n<div class=\"bg-matte theme-extra-footer padding overflow\" style=\"background-image: url(https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/TAOL_Backgrounds_2025_Round_footer.jpg);\" data-parallax=\"move\" data-parallax-anchor=\"true\" id=\"contact-the-art-of-light\">\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row theme-extra-footer-row\">\r\n            <div class=\"content-wrapper col-12-7\">\r\n                <h2>Here&#8217;s how to contact us.<\/h2>\r\n                <p><br><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"mailto:info@theartoflight.nl\">info@theartoflight.nl<\/a><br \/>\n<a href=\"tel:+31085